Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月15日  ‘日照良好’
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要想去做  早起之类的也是做得到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长好像还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对校长保密哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止对你发了不少火  真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后还请你自由随意地  竭尽所能大胆发挥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做早操了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  你也要来一起做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感觉能舒展筋骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒…你…了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容不灿烂点可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得不够甜美的话  是会被扣分的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在睡着呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天结束啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师们好像下午要开会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去后要做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先去吃完午饭再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去食堂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有空位啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去买饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐  宫子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选了猪排饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要去买饭  要一起吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和同班的同学一起吃  已经帮我占好位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那荠殿下呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  今天没在学校看到她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠已经先回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？只有一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  快上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人回家真是少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  只是东西忘在教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回教室取东西  所以晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…那就无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你那说话方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那班级怎么样？能好好相处吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说怎么样…  没什么变化啊  又没换班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就到这里了  谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够陪我这一程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是顺路而已  顺路啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…明天见！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好出门的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安  中午承蒙关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的  我想去买窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这附近哪里有卖的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗帘…哪里有卖呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐和寻学姐出门了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠的话  可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦  小荠是本地人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「ジモティー」俗語，意為本地人。）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基莫提？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义大利人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗帘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有没有什么推荐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“I'm home”应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“I'm home”是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…就是类似综合性超市的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有卖各种各样的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  卖各种各样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有平底锅  垃圾袋  厨柜  螺丝  花盆等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有精灵先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  还让你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店的位置口头上很难说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问下  我们也能一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  你这段时期窗帘是怎么弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用的是从家里带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但长度不合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很在意的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  躲进那边的窗帘里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要偷东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30厘米  和刚才的加起来总长是180厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  一百日元的卷尺真是太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃学姐  能过来一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够量出来耶  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经认不出路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐来短信说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“现在正在逛画具店  有什么想要的东西吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画具店是哪里的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在邻镇大型百货商场里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  虽然没进去过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的画具店很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我也去瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天上了吉野屋老师的课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是素描课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师还说要当模特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“只要大家开口  要老师裸体都行！”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是吉野屋老师嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没穿奇怪的服装吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就换上了轻飘飘的那种衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过被校长发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是太悲剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算躲到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里  “I'm home”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“基莫提”人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像能做出些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“什么”是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安全帽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种专业物品光看看就会感觉很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“I'm home”真不是盖的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾的种类很齐全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是也买些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也想要些小毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是链锯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种规格应有尽有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有趣呢  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伐木工？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  有好多笔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不怎么想迈腿前进呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就在这里等你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为学姐的我得想点办法才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候如果是少女漫画的话会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  乃莉佩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗帘的颜色还是准备选蓝色系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了～平时总是不自觉地选蓝色系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次想选个不一样的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我有说过我喜欢蓝色系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身边不是有很多蓝色系的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子学姐真是个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还没到窗帘专卖区的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由得就拿了很多东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  要用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠各式各样的都买了些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…矿泉水  润唇膏  柔软剂  胶带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有毛巾和电池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是些随处可买到的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到窗帘专卖区了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种类真不少呢  真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备买张蕾丝窗帘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  今天就只买普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  由乃亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾丝女王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  那身装扮看起来就像是个新娘似的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意宣誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠  你觉得哪个比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与…与其问我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问由乃学姐和宫子学姐是不是更…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不是美术科
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也谈不上什么审美…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得你那种想法很片面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是说进了美术科就会全都有很好的审美感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才进美术科来学习的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审美不就是需要慢慢磨练的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容分说地擅自认为有没有审美感不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的话  应该会选这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱  就选这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  貌似决定了呢  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  不要偷偷摸摸地往这边看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是房东吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东也来买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想种些什么东西试试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  暖阳庄也有个院子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  大家一起来种点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭菜园可是很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜园…能收获蔬菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能多一个配菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么做吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么草率地决定没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  能健康茁壮地成长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起齐心合力加油做吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能也不错呢  种得好的话也会很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  既然由大家来种的话  我就乐得清闲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果丰收的话就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是期待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉助同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条旧的窗帘能给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以啦  是要用来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我那房间没有窗帘…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一年来你是怎么过来的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫的房间是用的百叶窗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很少放下来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天的时候弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  寻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沙英学姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  那个大袋子里的是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？由于太贵了平时不怎么买
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在车站前的药店里卖得超～便宜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  小荠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐也是因为喜欢那个花纹才买的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是因为喜欢那个花纹才买的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还买了这个回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕃茄的幼苗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得茄子和黄瓜也不错的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是以表决的方式决定买蕃茄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很好嘛  就种种看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～我铲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果累了的话就尽管说  我来换手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠  我们去打水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这是小宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披萨～意面～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义大利蔬菜浓汤  炖蕃茄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太心急了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳烦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看看电视吧  晚饭还在做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭的话  我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不留下来吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家的份都做进去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐的手艺可是没的说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  再搬一个桌子来比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  这次有六个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去拿我房间里的那张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请大家看这个玄关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这玄关都和我的家差不多大小了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真太棒了  寻学姐的手艺真的超赞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是否合你们胃口  尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  不用客气多吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻经常给我们做饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻可是无所不能的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知就让妈妈教我马铃薯炖肉的做法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐也能够教你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我可以帮忙试味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做的料理会一点点增加的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么过来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还完全习惯不了一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要上学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得真的是很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小荠的节奏慢慢习惯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去过食堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去之前先碰下头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…铃一响就在楼梯口见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠还有乃莉她们  从今往后还有许多的事要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小荠她们俩肯定能相处得很融洽的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕃茄如果能丰收的话就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月15日  ‘完’  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说说女孩子会喜欢什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  吃饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪亮亮的饰品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有可爱的洋装
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:23:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油满塞的栗子蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓冰淇淋甜点和热呼呼的豆沙包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.62,0:23:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好吃的东西吃了都是会发胖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:23:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:24:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘4月20日  女生的感受’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘1月31日  直言不讳’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在山吹高中里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来看哦
